detail小小....<br />\n其中有一段回憶係疑似男主比自己老母坐爆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結局都算係good end黎<br />\n以前係布卡睇過"},{"pid":"c4a3acef1bd650f663defd773e798ef86d99ef9e","tid":26580,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T21:48:34.000Z","msg":"尋找身體 ? <br />\n<img src=\"http://99770.co/wp-content/uploads/a04cj84wj6uq04/4234/010//001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F99770.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fa04cj84wj6uq04%2F4234%2F010%2F%2F001.jpg&h=af62f23f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76cc19c29c05607842cf3cb9fa9107b5786f8435","tid":26580,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T21:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋找身體 ? <br />\n<img src=\"http://99770.co/wp-content/uploads/a04cj84wj6uq04/4234/010//001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F99770.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fa04cj84wj6uq04%2F4234%2F010%2F%2F001.jpg&h=af62f23f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係.....<br />\n我盡量回憶一下.....<br />\n一開波 成班player係個課室入面<br />\n有個冇左個頭 個「頭」個位好似部水機咁<br />\n有個好似冇左對眼<br />\n有個冇左個心臟 好似用機械定唔知乜當心臟用<br />\n仲有幾個我唔記得係冇左乜野<br />\n而得男主係所有野正常 淨係失憶"},{"pid":"45ea6ec033812006b7a317f6b4d31f5d1dc2f1ba","tid":26580,"uid":5186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T22:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8141ad11f0ac6bf861a94881960f1c9d7438635","tid":26580,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T22:02:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0223059b172e726de5866c09f7e811370c0b256","tid":26580,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T22:04:28.000Z","msg":"木偶代碼  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32df66f97b74bbfc966c82bcd5282ab596566e7f","tid":26580,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T22:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>木偶代碼  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啊